dallas'' star victoria principal said she came to the general assembly with a constituency of her own _ 600,000 kentucky arthritis sufferers
miss principal, who plays pam ewing on the cbs tv show, appeared before senate committees thursday in her role as spokeswoman and lobbyist for the national arthritis foundation
the beverly hills, calif., actress was pushing for passage of a senate bill to make expensive anti-arthritis drugs available by prescription to medicaid patients without prior approval by the state social services agency
gov. wallace wilkinson made it academic, ordering a policy change to do what the bill seeks
