so you don't get angry and bitter when you get defeated. you pick yourself back up and get back on the horse and go on and win the next election.''
but in lexington, ky., dole shrugged off bush
we're ready to go. we're ready for the next round in south dakota and minnesota and we'll see who wins those two. we'll see who's dispirited wednesday morning next week,'' he said
